# Perú Inolvidable - Souvenir shop management system

Perú Inolvidable is a Java web application to manage a souvenir shop with inventory management, chat box, shopping cart and payments.

## Installation

Use the system version control [git](https://git-scm.com/) to install Perú Inolvidable

```bash
git clone https://github.com/alexanderdoma/souvenir-shop.git
```

## Contributing

Pull requests are welcome. For major changes, please open an issue first
to discuss what you would like to change.

Please make sure to update tests as appropriate.
